<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

        <!-- HTML Meta Tags -->
        <title>Open Domains</title>
        <meta name="description" content="Free subdomains for personal sites, open-source projects, and more.">
        <meta property="og:title" content="Open Domains">
        <meta property="og:description" content="Free subdomains for personal sites, open-source projects, and more.">
        <meta property="og:image" content="/assets/open-domains.net.png">
        <meta property="og:url" content="https://open-domains.net">
        <meta property="og:type" content="website">
        <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
        <meta name="twitter:title" content="Open Domains">
        <meta name="twitter:description" content="Free subdomains for personal sites, open-source projects, and more.">
        <meta name="twitter:image" content="/assets/open-domains.net.png">
        <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-title" content="Open Domains">
        <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
        <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-status-bar-style" content="black-translucent">
        <meta name="theme-color" content="#111827">

        <!-- Favicon -->
        <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/assets/logo.png" type="image/x-icon">

        <!-- Scripts -->
        <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/typed.js@2.0.12"></script>
    </head>

    <body class="p-8 max-w-xl m-auto bg-gray-900 text-white text-center">
        <header class="mt-10">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold">Open Domains</h1>
            <h2 class="font-semibold">Free subdomains for personal sites, open-source projects, and more.</h2>

            <div class="mt-10">
                <h3 class="inline font-bold text-3xl"><span class="typed"></span></h3>
            </div>
        </header>

        <main class="mt-10">
            <p class="mt-3"><a class="border-b font-bold hover:border-none" >Open Domains</a> is a service where you can register subdomains for free. Our service offers the opportunity to register subdomains such as <code class="bg-slate-700 py-1 px-2 rounded text-sm">foo.is-cool.dev</code> or <code class="bg-slate-700 py-1 px-2 rounded text-sm">bar.is-not-a.dev</code> and more! Our subdomains support the use of A, AAAA, CNAME, MX, NS and TXT records.</p>

            <div class="mt-10">
                <a href="/register" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded">Register</a>
                <a href="/login" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded">Login</a>
            </div>

        </main>

        <footer class="mt-8 mb-20 text">
            <p>&copy; <script>document.write(new Date().getFullYear())</script> <a class="border-b font-semibold hover:border-none" href="https://github.com/open-domains/register">Open Domains</a> - All Rights Reserved.</p>
            <br>
            <p>A project by <a class="border-b font-semibold hover:border-none" href="https://andrewstech.me">Andrewstech</a>.</p>
            <p>Website made by <a class="border-b font-semibold hover:border-none" href="https://williamharrison.dev">William Harrison</a>.</p>
        </footer>

        <script>
            var typed = new Typed(".typed", {
                strings: ["foo.is-cool.dev", "bar.is-local.org", "foo.is-not-a.dev", "bar.localplayer.dev"],
                typeSpeed: 120,
                smartBackspace: false,
                loop: true
            });
        </script>
    </body>
</html>